Title: Debts and Accounts
Writer: Graham Yost (developed for television by), Chris Provenzano, Elmore Leonard (based on the short story "Fire in the Hole"), Benjamin Cavell (story editor)
Actors: Timothy Olyphant, Nick Searcy, Joelle Carter, Jacob Pitts
Plot: As Winona begins divorce proceedings, Raylan begins to contemplate his future as a marshal. Meanwhile, Dicky Bennett takes exception to his family's new business arrangement with Boyd Crowder.
